title: Very crateful: Pittsburgh Police K-9 unit dogs get new, safer kennels
text:
Published By: Pittsburgh Post: Local - Today 
The 22 dogs in the Pittsburgh Bureau of Police K-9 Unit are moving up to military-grade transport with new collapsible metal crates unveiled...
